  "title": "Product Manager (B2B, IT Security/Network)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Oversee and expand the portfolio of cybersecurity products and related technical services to drive market growth andprofitability.</li><li>Collaborate with sales and operations teams to enhance service quality, optimize product delivery, and develop competitive pricingstrategies.</li><li>Conduct market research, analyze trends, and provide actionable insights for medium- and long-term business planning.</li><li>Identify and evaluate potential partner relationships tosupport product adoption and maximize market reach.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Diploma or degree in IT, Computer Science, or related field; candidates without IT qualifications must have 2–3 years of relevant sales experience.</li><li>Fresh graduates with strong motivation and willingness to\nlearn, or professionals with sales experience in other industries, are encouraged to apply.</li><li>Proven ability to manage products, services, and technical solutions in IT or cybersecurity environments.</li><li>Strong analytical, leadership, and problem-solving skills\nwith excellent interpersonal and communication abilities.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email yourdetailed resume in <strong>MS Word</strong> to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will benotified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our websiteat <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R25158160</p>",
